# Unity Package Manager (UPM) - Manifest 管理規範

## 1. 概述
本文件定義 Unity 專案中使用 manifest.json 管理套件的標準流程。

## 2. manifest.json 位置
/Packages/manifest.json

## 3. 基本結構
{
  "dependencies": {}
}

## 4. 套件來源類型

### Unity 官方 Registry
{
  "dependencies": {
    "com.unity.cinemachine": "2.9.7"
  }
}

### Git 套件
{
  "dependencies": {
    "com.cysharp.unitask": "https://github.com/Cysharp/UniTask.git#2.5.4"
  }
}

### Git 子資料夾
{
  "dependencies": {
    "com.company.mypackage": "https://github.com/company/repo.git?path=Packages/mypackage"
  }
}

### 本地套件
{
  "dependencies": {
    "com.mycompany.mylib": "file:../MyLib"
  }
}

### Scoped Registry
{
  "scopedRegistries": [
    {
      "name": "My Registry",
      "url": "https://registry.mycompany.com",
      "scopes": ["com.mycompany"]
    }
  ],
  "dependencies": {
    "com.mycompany.mypackage": "1.0.0"
  }
}
